(40, 16, 12, 40, 5, 20, 20, 'doctrine of the Pharisees', 'Righteousness and Doctrine Connection', 'This connection highlights the emphasis on the doctrine of the Pharisees, which is linked to their righteousness. Both passages address the standards of righteousness expected from followers, contrasting Jesus'' teachings with those of the Pharisees.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
