(40, 16, 12, 40, 15, 4, 9, 'doctrine of the Pharisees and of the Sadducees', 'Doctrine of the Pharisees', 'Both passages emphasize the conflict between God''s commandments and human traditions. In Matthew 16:12, Jesus warns against the ''doctrine of the Pharisees,'' while Matthew 15:4-9 illustrates how their traditions undermine God''s commands.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
